Travel Agent ‚Äì Travel Information Chatbot
1Ô∏è‚É£ Introduction

Travel Agent is a web-based chatbot application developed using Python (Flask), HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
The system provides instant travel-related information such as visa requirements, vaccination details, currency information, emergency contacts, and local customs.

The main objective of this project is to create an intelligent travel assistance system that reduces dependency on manual travel agents and provides quick and structured travel guidance.

2Ô∏è‚É£ Problem Statement

Travelers often face difficulty in finding reliable and structured travel information such as:

Visa requirements

Required vaccinations

Currency details

Emergency contact numbers

Local customs

Searching this information manually can be time-consuming and confusing.

The solution is to develop a chatbot that provides instant travel information in a simple interactive format.

3Ô∏è‚É£ Objectives

To develop an interactive travel information chatbot

To provide visa and travel requirement details

To implement a structured YES/NO conversation flow

To reduce travel agent workload

To improve traveler satisfaction

4Ô∏è‚É£ Technologies Used
Technology	Purpose
Python	Backend programming
Flask	Web framework
HTML	Structure of webpage
CSS	Styling and UI design
JavaScript	Frontend interactivity
JSON	Data exchange format
5Ô∏è‚É£ System Architecture

The system follows a client-server architecture:

User (Browser)
‚¨á
Frontend (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)
‚¨á
Flask Backend (app.py)
‚¨á
Destination Data Dictionary
‚¨á
Response sent back to User

6Ô∏è‚É£ Working of the System

User opens the chatbot in the browser.

Bot displays menu options:

Check Visa

Travel Info

Help

User selects an option.

If destination is entered:

Backend checks destination dictionary.

Retrieves required travel details.

Bot displays:

Visa Required (YES/NO)

Vaccination Info

Currency

Emergency Contact

Local Customs

User can restart conversation anytime.

7Ô∏è‚É£ Features

